976A\">b</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">example</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">();</span></span></code><button class=\"copy\" data-lang=\"javascript\" title=\"Copy code\">Copy</button></pre>\n",
