  {
    "question": "<p>什么是<strong>闭包 (Closure)</strong>？</p>\n",
    "answer": "<p>闭包是一个函数和它周围状态（<strong>词法环境</strong>）的引用捆绑在一起形成的组合。</p>\n"
  },
  {
    "question": "<p>从内存管理（GC）的角度看，闭包的本质是什么？</p>\n",
    "answer": "<p>当外部函数执行完毕且其执行上下文被销毁后，如果内部函数仍引用了外部函数的变量，这些变量会<strong>保存在内存中</strong>（堆），而不会被垃圾回收机制（GC）回收。</p>\n"
  },
  {
    "question": "<p>在以下代码中，变量 <code>count</code> 最终存储在哪里？为什么？</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark not-prose\" style=\"--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">function</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> createCounter</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">()</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"indent\">  </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">let</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> count</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 0</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"indent\">  </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">return</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> function</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> ()</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"indent\">  </span><span class=\"indent\">  </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">return</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> ++</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">count</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"indent\">  </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">};</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">const</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> counter</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> createCounter</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">();</span></span></code><button class=\"copy\" data-lang=\"javascript\" title=\"Copy code\">Copy</button></pre>\n",
    "answer": "<p>存储在<strong>堆内存 (Heap)</strong> 中。\n原因：<code>createCounter</code> 执行完后，其执行上下文虽出栈，但内部匿名函数通过闭包引用了 <code>count</code>，导致 <code>count</code> 被捕获到堆中以供后续调用。</p>\n"
